name: Laura Shinade
description:
i am pleasant, sensual, romantic woman.I am very easy-going girl with my outlook on life. I try to combine positive and realistic views on different things. I am modest girl but in the same time I like to be in the spotlight. I am very sociable person and now I am open to dialogue
I want to be with man, who is open for feelings, love, passion. Who is calm, but likes to laugh and to have fun a lot. I want someone who is mature, kind, not afraid of being honest and willing to feel what the love is.. and to share this feeling. Are you smiling now, because it is about you and you want the same? Please, let me know about it.. I am waiting for you.
